    <item>
      <title>众议院议长约翰逊向民主党求助以避免政府关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/speaker-johnson-turns-to-democrats-to-avert-government-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院周三避免了一场对政治造成损害的政府关门，并在议员们从华盛顿赶往 11 月大选之前进行最后的竞选活动之前迅速通过了一项短期联邦拨款法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/speaker-johnson-turns-to-democrats-to-avert-government-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 20:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在经济演讲中将自己塑造为亲劳工“资本家”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-casts-herself-as-pro-labor-capitalist-in-economic-pitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯誓言要成为企业高管和员工的盟友，这位民主党总统候选人概述了她对“机会经济”的愿景，即资助新行业投资并建设中产阶级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-casts-herself-as-pro-labor-capitalist-in-economic-pitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 20:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AOC 呼吁纽约市长亚当斯在调查期间辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/aoc-calls-for-new-york-mayor-adams-to-resign-amid-investigations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚历山大·奥卡西奥·科尔特斯是纽约国会代表团中最受瞩目的议员之一，她要求纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯下台，理由是他的政府面临越来越多的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/aoc-calls-for-new-york-mayor-adams-to-resign-amid-investigations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 19:55:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多成功躲过波利耶夫雷提前举行大选的企图</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trudeau-survives-attempt-to-force-snap-election-by-poilievre</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的主要政治对手试图在周三提前举行选举，但由于缺乏议会其他反对党的支持，这一努力失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trudeau-survives-attempt-to-force-snap-election-by-poilievre</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 19:49:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔火灾威胁富裕社区，迫使总统回家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ecuador-fires-threaten-rich-neighborhoods-force-president-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基多的富裕社区仍然面临火灾威胁，在消防员与厄瓜多尔首都的森林大火搏斗之际，学校已转为在线教学，直至本周末。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ecuador-fires-threaten-rich-neighborhoods-force-president-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 19:31:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利国会支持立法创造数十亿新税收收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chile-congress-backs-bill-generating-billions-in-new-tax-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利立法者最终批准了一项打击逃税、增加政府收入的立法，在总统加布里埃尔·博里奇公布 2025 年预算前几天，这项法案获得了胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chile-congress-backs-bill-generating-billions-in-new-tax-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 18:49:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与盟友合作制止黎巴嫩以色列与真主党的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-working-with-allies-to-halt-israel-hezbollah-war-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正与法国和英国等盟友合作，提出一项建议，以阻止以色列军队与黎巴嫩真主党武装分子之间的冲突升级。此次冲突已造成数百人死亡，并有可能引发更大范围的中东冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-working-with-allies-to-halt-israel-hezbollah-war-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰援助申请遭遇竞选冲突 特朗普猛烈抨击泽连斯基</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/zelenskiy-s-push-for-support-runs-into-us-campaign-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普严厉批评弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基对他的批评并拒绝与莫斯科达成结束冲突的协议，这给乌克兰总统最近为抵抗俄罗斯入侵而争取更多援助的努力蒙上了阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/zelenskiy-s-push-for-support-runs-into-us-campaign-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 16:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称中国推动和平，却帮助俄罗斯发动战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/zelenskiy-says-china-pushing-peace-while-aiding-putin-s-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基更加尖锐地批评中国影响与俄罗斯战争的努力，指责北京推行有缺陷的和平计划，同时帮助莫斯科攻击核基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/zelenskiy-says-china-pushing-peace-while-aiding-putin-s-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 15:49:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
